videos.description: Brianna Fraser makes the nice move and finishes the layup after drawing the foul, giving Maryland the early lead.
videos.headline: Maryland's Fraser works her way in for and-1 layup

videos.description: Brionna Jones finishes in the lane and then Destiny Slocum hits the 3-pointer to extend Maryland's lead over Iowa.
videos.headline: Maryland scoring multiple ways to build lead

videos.description: Brionna Jones makes the layup and then blocks the shot on the defensive end, helping Maryland stay in front of Iowa.
videos.headline: Maryland's Jones getting it done on both ends

videos.description: Iowa's Tania Davis sells the fake pass to make the transition layup against Maryland.
videos.headline: Iowa's Davis fakes out defender for great finish

videos.description: Destiny Slocum use the spin move to get free and find Stephanie Jones for the easy layup, extending Maryland's lead over Iowa.
videos.headline: Maryland's Slocum spins around defender for to set up Jones for bucket

videos.description: Maryland's Brionna Jones works through contact for the bucket down low, increasing the Terrapins' lead over Iowa
videos.headline: Marlyand extends lead with and-1 layup

videos.description: Destiny Slocum finds Brianna Fraser with the great entry pass, and Fraser responds by making another and-1 layup for Maryland.
videos.headline: Maryland's Slocum continues to drop dimes

videos.description: Maryland's Brionna Jones talks about her 28 point performance against Iowa
videos.headline: Maryland's Brionna Jones happy about performance in win over Iowa
